title: Distance to GP and Limiting Long-term illness in Nottingham City
name: Distance to GP and Limiting Long-term illness in Nottingham City
description: This is derived from the UK 2001 census data; the spatial units are Lower Super Output Areas (LSOA); for each LSOA two fields are given: Limiting Long-term illness, and Distance to General Practise surgery (averaged for the population within each LSOA)
